##Rebuilt Scouting App 2026 (Rebuilt)

An Android-based robotics scouting application designed for FRC Team 167 (Iowa City Robotics). This app allows scouts to collect match data offline and export it via JSON to a USB drive for analysis.
This project uses a modular Architecture. The goal is to make the app easy to update for future seasons (2027+) without rewriting complex Java logic.

